<div class="container container-main">
	<div class="row">

		<div class="col-12">

			<h1 class="title-text">@ViewBag.Subtitle</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="card-btn-text col-md-6">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-4 col-md-3">
					<a class="btn btn-default btn-lg" href="http://www.CheckOutMyStuff.net" target="_blank">
						<img src="~/Images/Check Out My Stuff Logo.png" alt="Check Out My Stuff Logo - checkbox shaped as an eye" width="50" />
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="col">
					<strong>Check Out My Stuff</strong> - A free library site for YOUR stuff that you want to loan out to people (just cause you can and you're nice).
					Sometimes I'll blog about code, here's one
					<a href="https://spilledmilkcom.wordpress.com/2016/09/11/endless-infinite-scrolling-using-jquery-and-net-mvc/" target="_blank"><strong>example</strong></a>.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="card-btn-text col-md-6">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-4 col-md-3">
					<a class="btn btn-default btn-lg" href="~/Apps/IdiotDriver" target="_blank">
						<img width="50" src="~/Images/Idiot Driver 300x300.jpg" alt="Idiot Driver Logo - car horn logo" width="50" />
					</a>
				</div>
				<div class="col">
					<strong>Idiot Driver</strong> - A voice driven twitter client to rant about idiots on the road.  Coming soon to the Apple Store and Google Play.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>

	<div class="row row-divider"> </div>
</div>